nuary, 2023,” Ikpeazu said.  Governor Okezie Ikpeazu of Abia State. By Ugochukwu Alaribe UMUAHIA- Abia State Governor, Dr. Okezie Ikpeazu, has stated that he won’t hand over to a successor who will learn on the job as governor of the state. He insisted that those aspiring to lead after him should not be persons… In "News" Governor Okezie Ikpeazu It is said that the primary responsibility of any government is to secure lives and property of the people in exchange for the citizens performing their own statutory responsibilities. To the glory of God, the Okezie Ikpeazu-led administration in Abia State can beat its chest as of… In "Viewpoint" A member of Abia State PDP Campaign Council, Chief John Okiyi Kalu has dismissed that Governor Okezie Ikpeazu is working for the presidential candidate of the All Progressives Congress, Bola Tinubu. In a statement he personally signed and made available to newsmen on Saturday, Okiyi Kalu said those speculating on… In "News"